imdb.plot outline: A lonely romantic girl from a backwater rural town Kluchi has a dream to find her true love and live together in a seashore house. The latter part is close to come to true, as she wears herself out working as a train conductor at days and a shop-girl at nights, saving the money. But the man she meets is only interested in her money.
